<import src="../../../common/storelist.wxml" />

<view class="container">
  <view class="dc-title">
    <view class="t-l">
      <view></view>选择</view>
    <view class="t-r" bindtap="rules">
      <icon type="info_circle" size="20" color="#333" />细则</view>
  </view>

  <view class="do-card clear" style="height:{{height}}px">
    <!-- 门店列表模版 -->
    <template is="storelist" data="{{height: height,dcStore: dcStore,storeIdx: storeIdx}}" />

    <view class="dc-select">
      <view class="d-cards" style="height:{{dcSHeight}}px">
        <scroll-view scroll-y enable-back-to-top style="height:{{dcSHeight}}px">
          <view class="select-c">
            <view class="cards">
              <navigator url="../../pages/now-docard/now-docard" hover-class="none">
                <image src="https://iservice.daqisoft.cn/Public/Home/images/docard3.png" lazy-load></image>
              </navigator>
              <view>铂金卡需充值2000元以上</view>
            </view>
            <view class="cards">
              <image src="https://iservice.daqisoft.cn/Public/Home/images/docard2.png" lazy-load></image>
              <view>铂金卡需充值2000元以上</view>
            </view>
            <view class="cards">
              <image src="https://iservice.daqisoft.cn/Public/Home/images/docard1.png" lazy-load></image>
              <view>铂金卡需充值2000元以上</view>
            </view>
            <view class="cards">
              <image src="https://iservice.daqisoft.cn/Public/Home/images/docard2.png" lazy-load></image>
              <view>铂金卡需充值2000元以上</view>
            </view>
            <view class="cards">
              <image src="https://iservice.daqisoft.cn/Public/Home/images/docard1.png" lazy-load></image>
              <view>铂金卡需充值2000元以上</view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </scroll-view>
      </view>
      <view class="s-info">
        <view class="s-info-c">
          <view class="s-info-b">
            <view>名称：和毅足道体育新城店</view>
            <view>电话：400-2039-6739</view>
            <view>地址：湖南省长沙市芙蓉区万家丽路宽寓大厦3206富士通邗晨</view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

</view>


<view class="mask" style="display:{{showMask ? 'block' : 'none'}}"></view>

<view class="rules" style="display:{{showMask ? 'block' : 'none'}}">
  <scroll-view scroll-y enable-back-to-top>
    <view class="close-r" bindtap="closeRules">×</view>
    <view class="rules-con">
      <view class="rules-t">金卡须知</view>
      <view class="rules-c">1、凭本卡消费，敬请结账时出示并输入密码；</view>
      <view class="rules-c">2、本卡可在和毅足道各直营子公司消费（详见店面海报）；</view>
      <view class="rules-c">3、主项消费享受金卡会员价优惠；</view>
      <view class="rules-c">4、本卡有效期为一年（以最后一次充值时间为起始日期）；</view>
      <view class="rules-c">5、一经售出概不退换、不兑现、不找零；有效期满后由开卡门店提供激活服务；</view>
      <view class="rules-c">6、本卡可按消费10元积1分参与积分奖励与兑换活动；</view>
      <view class="rules-c">7、具体用卡规定详见前台《和毅足道贵宾卡使用指南》；</view>
      <view class="rules-c">8、本店在法律许可范围内保留对此卡消费细则的最终解释权和修改权。</view>
